lead_paragraph: Jose Mourinho's announcement that Zlatan Ibrahimovic will stay at Manchester United for a second season was a bold statement of faith in a striker still trying to prove himself in England.

headline.print_headline: Mourinho Ties His Fate to Ibrahimovic at United
